title: Emily Ramshaw: On Launching a Nonprofit Amid Covid-19
description: Emily Ramshaw, cofounder of women-focused nonprofit media company the 19th*, tells WSJ's Veronica Dagher how she's adapted her organization to the coronavirus and why the untold stories of the female electorate matter.
